''[[Al-Masry Al-Youm]]''. 17 May 2011.</ref> At least two of the wounded had been shot in head and chest by Egyptian forces, and at least two of those arrested were well known for their [[Twitter]]s during the [[2011 Egyptian revolution]].<ref name=Bikya/> All those who were arrested faced military trials and were later freed.
